{"title":"歌戎冠秀","authors":["纪初阳"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌戎冠秀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪初阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在旧社会里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪一把……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手看不见巴掌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但咬着牙根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他活得刚强不倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀的眼睛被点亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心开了花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着共产党；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要给人民打天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那些苦年月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是用武装反“扫荡”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们英雄的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺着胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用自己的奶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养护着英雄的儿女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她老啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的手还不停；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿行千里母担心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见叶落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不知孩子们的衣裳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薄不薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不知孩子们的鞋底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漏没漏？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民的天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍一针针串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍一针针缝……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们的好老人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年四季，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她敲打吊在她门前的那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召群众："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱打粮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碾最好的米送前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝最结实的鞋子给子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟兵穿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弟兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻山越岭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠的打敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好了伤疤忘不了痛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记着人民的山和水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记着好母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀进了北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在人民政协会议上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开大家庭会议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商量建国的大事情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了朱总司令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛里闪着光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民坐了天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天下是血打的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天下是铁打的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系着千千万万母亲的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许破坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许动撼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这就是我们工人农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民开天辟地的大翻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她坐在人民的宫殿里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐稳这天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要团结一心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把敌人消灭干净！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}